### Design System Requirements

#### Color Palette (Dark Theme)

- Background: Black (#000) / Anthracite (#1a1a1a)
- Text: White (#fff) / Silver (#c0c0c0)
- Accent: Mercedes Blue (#00adef) sparingly
- Border: Dark gray (#2a2a2a)

#### Typography

- Use Inter or similar clean sans-serif
- Headings: Large, bold, plenty of whitespace
- Body: 16px base, 1.5-1.6 line height
- Premium feel: Generous letter spacing on headings

#### Spacing

- Large white space between sections (120px-160px)
- Generous padding (80px-100px on desktop)
- Consistent internal spacing system (8px base)

#### Components Style

- Minimal borders, use subtle shadows
- Rounded corners (8px-12px)
- Smooth transitions (300ms ease)
- Hover states: Subtle scale (1.02) or opacity (0.9)

