## Content Guidelines

### Images

- Only use HIGH-QUALITY, REAL photos
- No stock photos or generic images
- Show actual workshop, equipment, projects
- Consistent editing style (slightly desaturated, professional)

### Copy Writing

- Professional, confident tone
- Technical accuracy (use correct Mercedes terminology)
- Bilingual: Professional English, natural Bulgarian
- Emphasize: Certification, OEM equipment, experience

### CTAs

- Primary: "Book Service" / "Запази Час"
- Secondary: "Contact Us" / "Свържи се с нас"
- Tertiary: "Learn More" / "Научи повече"

## Performance Targets

- Lighthouse Score: 95+ on all metrics
- First Contentful Paint: < 1.5s
- Time to Interactive: < 3s
- No layout shift (CLS: 0)

## Accessibility

- Semantic HTML5 elements
- ARIA labels on interactive elements
- Keyboard navigation support
- Alt text on all images
- Sufficient color contrast (WCAG AA)

## Git Workflow

- Commit messages: `feat:`, `fix:`, `style:`, `refactor:`
- One feature per branch
- Test builds before committing

## Testing Checklist

- [ ] All pages render in both languages
